1. *Plaži* su savršeno mesto za letovanje. (Beaches are the perfect place for vacation.)
2. Ovi lepi *plaži* privlače turiste iz celog sveta. (These beautiful beaches attract tourists from all over the world.)
3. Naša porodica provodi letnje praznike na *plaži*. (Our family spends the summer holidays on the beach.)
4. Nije bilo teško pronaći mesto za sunčanje na *plaži*. (It was not difficult to find a place to sunbathe on the beach.)
5. Ovog leta htela bih da posetim neke egzotične *plaže*. (This summer I would like to visit some exotic beaches.)